\subsection{Artefact Design}
The artefact produced in this project is an interactive web-based dashboard built 
using Python. The dashboard allows a user to upload their historical
sales data in CSV format, select a forecasting model and receive a weekly demand 
forecast together with an explanation of the prediction. The design follows the 
requirements of the MoSCoW analysis in the Business Understanding Chapter: it 
must be usable by non-technical users, provide explanations for every forecast and 
support multiple model options.
